Team2_Capstone/
│
├── .env                       # (Private) Store OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-..." here
├── requirements.txt           # List of libraries to install
├── app.py                     # (Main) Streamlit UI - ONLY ONE PERSON touches this primarily
│
└── agents/                    # (Folder) Where the team writes logic
    ├── __init__.py            # (Empty File) Needed to make this a Python package
    ├── utils.py               # Shared tools (formatting, charts)
    ├── data_pipeline.py       # MEMBER 1 (Data): Ingestion & Classification logic
    ├── fraud_agent.py         # MEMBER 2 (Biz Logic): Fraud detection logic
    ├── policy_agent.py        # MEMBER 3 (Biz Logic): Policy checking logic
    └── customer_agent.py      # MEMBER 4 (Customer): Chatbot & Tone logic